I’m editing the code for the robot today, and suddenly i noticed a red squiggle under “Robot” in the class declaration:

class Robot : public frc::TimedRobot {
...
}

when i mouse over the squiggle, it gives me the error message:

exception specification for implicitly declared virtual function “Robot::~Robot” is incompatible with that of overridden function “frc::TimedRobot::~TimedRobot”

What could be causing this issue?

For reference, I’m trying to use the timed robot skeleton WPI project in c++
